{"tid":1438100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚黃大仙狗狗轉左策略","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:35.000Z","uid":127735,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb64b221b480a1765299ccf706fb59bb232686bd","tid":1438100,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"唔再長期企係到，無必要時上曬狗車坐底休息回氣，有必要時先出黎，再出埋真狗又慳到人手又有真狗黎咬人。<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地知道呢班係街坊一定唔會衝，宜家似係學精左唔再一味亂清場。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣就營造唔到一個所謂既「警民衝突」情景，佢地心知宜家發生「警民衝突」一定會偏幫市民果邊，愈硬清場盞愈整到自己既形象下滑。<br />\n<br />\n當然唔排除可能今日有燒街衣，班狗狗唔敢亂黎，怕有純街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之我地繼續用心理攻擊同光線光擊就岩既啦，高層換老屎忽唔代表前線狗狗換左腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91361313c423569cf5f155dca4a073cc3b3af24","tid":1438100,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"765dcd5e9424dd5d5c9435a22806c056e38dd02f","tid":1438100,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"推比黃大仙街坊知"},{"pid":"03f037f1494ca204ee1221b474a6c4d3168172b9","tid":1438100,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNxu1GJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNxu1GJ.jpg&h=64932c27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EaXq8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EaXq8p.jpg&h=a1242c6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QJRCLw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QJRCLw.jpg&h=22e07ece&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVOuhe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVOuhe4.jpg&h=a6d636f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbOFoU5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi